1 of c arrying on the duties of the Commission. The Commission shall
2 have sole, entire and exclusive authority of the disposition for all
3 public records and archives of state officers, departments, boards,
4 commissions, agencies and institutions of this state. The authority
5 herein granted shall not apply to records and archives of political
6 subdivisions of the state; provided, however, Section 305 et seq. of
7 this title shall not apply to the confidential records and files of
8 the Oklahoma Tax Commission which are exempt from all provisions of
9 this act.
